<emphasis box="[1275,1440,1657,1681]" italics="true" pageId="36" pageNumber="35">Cobalus arita</emphasis>
Schaus, 1902
</taxonomicName>
) (
<figureCitation box="[376,507,1689,1713]" captionStart-0="Figure 11" captionStart-1="Figure 12" captionStartId-0="29.[192,275,1330,1352]" captionStartId-1="31.[192,275,1330,1352]" captionTargetBox-0="[195,1438,214,1295]" captionTargetBox-1="[194,1440,214,1295]" captionTargetId-0="figure@29.[194,1442,213,1296]" captionTargetId-1="figure@31.[192,1440,213,1296]" captionTargetPageId-0="29" captionTargetPageId-1="31" captionText-0="Figure 11. Nuclear genome and Z chromosome trees of Moncina and relatives. See Fig. 2 legend for notations." captionText-1="Figure 12. Mitochondrial genome and COI barcode trees of Moncina and relatives. See Fig. 2 legend for notations." figureDoi-0="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3677257" figureDoi-1="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3677259" httpUri-0="https://zenodo.org/record/3677257/files/figure.png" httpUri-1="https://zenodo.org/record/3677259/files/figure.png" pageId="36" pageNumber="35">Fig. 11â€“12</figureCitation>
). For instance, COI barcodes of the 
<typeStatus box="[936,989,1689,1713]" pageId="36" pageNumber="35">type</typeStatus>
